{"tid":1584135,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"9月21日今日為國際和平日","createTime":"2019-09-21T03:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T03:18:43.000Z","uid":239842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"68e833c2a9db2b2f09d7edf20e60a226cc0b0148","tid":1584135,"uid":239842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T03:15:11.000Z","msg":"中意打國際戰線嘅同路人會唔會考慮一下調整行動方向，甚至借左呢一點調轉頭製造番對自己有利嘅輿論？<br />\n<br />\n當然，如果大家都認為呢樣野冇人知冇需要理，就由佢啦。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內容轉自維基百科<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hant/国际和平日\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hant%2F%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E6%97%A5&d=ekRw3fL0jih6ME0SbOEd7ygGTjEty4RfxMaQWzCDCUQ%3D&h=d6406662\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hant/国际和平日</a><br />\n<br />\n2001年9月7日，聯合國大會通過55/282號決議，決定自2002年起，國際和平日為9月21日。決議中提到：「宣布此後，國際和平日應成為全球停火和非暴力日，並邀請所有國家和人民在這一天停止敵對行動。」55/282號決議還邀請所有會員國、聯合國系統各組織、區域組織和非政府組織以及個人以各種適當方式（包括教育和公眾宣傳）慶祝國際和平日並同聯合國合作實現全球停火。"},{"pid":"e9263dfa645862d345e29c83c741f0cced1c8ae8","tid":1584135,"uid":239842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T03:15:45.000Z","msg":"自推十次 1/10"},{"pid":"62ba555caf65016bdc519c5faea4a86d57f25c33","tid":1584135,"uid":239842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T03:16:22.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"02d7bb5fa987bd69d593cb8e1278ca189da348ad","tid":1584135,"uid":239842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T03:16:40.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"2483b88215e4107900779f3fa5f32e4c4429e540","tid":1584135,"uid":239842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T03:16:53.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"03b64c8217896327049b27d41706d998ccda4be3","tid":1584135,"uid":239842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T03:17:13.000Z","msg":"自推 5/10"},{"pid":"f182ab99c376120791a638cf5189ac6293aa950f","tid":1584135,"uid":476